name: Nick Fox-Gieg - Beastie2.Bin (1995, GIF version)
description: Beastie2.Bin, by Nick Fox-Gieg, compiled from a series of screenshots taken in the SheepShaver Mac emulator, restoring an otherwise unviewable and unexportable Swivel 3D model created in 1995. This is the official GIF version, released 17 July 2021.
